snippet.title: suteF - Trailer
snippet.description:
game by Ted Lauterbach - http://www.rottentater.com/sutef
ted.lauterbach@gmail.com

suteF is the sequel to my atmospheric puzzle game, Fetus. I've developed it using Game Maker 8.0 Pro over the course of the last 5 months. A final build is scheduled to be complete for the 2011 Student IGF and released soon after.
